{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"y","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/y","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG属性リファレンスホームへ</a></p>\n<p>この属性はユーザー座標系のy軸座標を指定します。この属性の正確な影響は各要素の座標に依存します。ほとんどの場合、この属性参照している要素の左上を原点とした長方形のx軸座標を示します（例外については個々の要素のドキュメントを参照してください）。</p>\n<p>値の明示がなければ、<strong>0</strong>として記入されたものとして、 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> と <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mask\"><code>&lt;mask&gt;</code></a> 要素に関しては <strong>-10%</strong> と記入されたものと解釈します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用可能な場所","title":"使用可能な場所","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">カテゴリ</th>\n   <td>なし</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">値</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/SVG/Content_type#coordinate\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/SVG/Content_type#Coordinate\">&lt;coordinate&gt;</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">アニメーション</th>\n   <td>可</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">標準文書</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/text.html#AltGlyphElementYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): altGlyph element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/interact.html#CursorElementYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): cursor element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/filters.html#fePointLightYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): fePointLight element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/filters.html#feSpotLightYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): feSpotLight element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/filters.html#FilterElementYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): filter element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/extend.html#ForeignObjectElementYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): foreignObject element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/text.html#GlyphRefElementYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): glyphRef element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/struct.html#ImageElementYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): image element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/pservers.html#PatternElementYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): pattern element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/shapes.html#RectElementYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): rect element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/struct.html#SVGElementYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): svg element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/text.html#TextElementYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): text element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/struct.html#UseElementYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): use element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/filters.html#FilterPrimitiveYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): Filter primitive</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/masking.html#MaskElementYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): mask element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/text.html#TSpanElementYAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): tspan element</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p><dl>\n\t<dt id=\"coordinate_2\">&lt;coordinate&gt;</dt>\n\t<dd>\n\t<p>&lt;coordinate&gt; は関連する軸に沿って (X 座標は X 軸に沿って、 Y 座標は Y 軸に沿って) ユーザー座標系の原点から所定の座標までの距離を指定します。その構文は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#length\">&lt;length&gt;</a> と同一です。</p>\n\n\t<p>SVG DOM 内では、 &lt;coordinate&gt; の値は <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGLength\"><code>SVGLength</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> もしくは <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGAnimatedLength\"><code>SVGAnimatedLength</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> で表現されます。</p>\n\t</dd>\n</dl><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"要素","title":"要素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>次の要素は <code>y</code> 属性を使用することができます。</p>\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/decs/Web/SVG/Element#FilterPrimitive\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Filter primitive elements</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/altGlyph\"><code>&lt;altGlyph&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/fePointLight\"><code>&lt;fePointLight&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpotLight\"><code>&lt;feSpotLight&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/foreignObject\"><code>&lt;foreignObject&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyphRef\"><code>&lt;glyphRef&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/pattern\"><code>&lt;pattern&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/rect\"><code>&lt;rect&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/use\"><code>&lt;use&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mask\"><code>&lt;mask&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"使用可能な場所","id":"使用可能な場所"},{"text":"要素","id":"要素"}],"summary":"« SVG属性リファレンスホームへ","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"y","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"y","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"y","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/svg/attribute/y","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/svg/attribute/y/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG: スケーラブルベクターグラフィック"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性リファレンス"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/y","title":"y"}],"pageTitle":"y - SVG: スケーラブルベクターグラフィック | MDN","noIndexing":false}}